
    A BLAZING fire left 500 people homeless in Chris Hani Park, Strand over the weekend.  The fire started in a shack that was vacant at about 5pm on Friday.“There was no one in that shack so it is hard to say what caused the fire but we suspect illegal connections. We tried to save some of our things but the fire spread too fast. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsthrSmaJy9uxIEut9ShGoueDy-cYhcvzR4QihM91QC7UOqdODqkm70zjkHMmDakVaDTxuofsWlPUM7-4Dcsm8CxhuKOFfKK1l_V5FRJ3yCXaMc1KffwNnH5zBhuruB8E0JGZRlL8PgHTzKegyX2qSjBRBhF_hpko19PnzNsvg0uPAH9DdxeIHI2x1aHpislO0tf-dbAvmmW3QwWdPALGwOQzTY7DaEHvruH7verzuA3blOAlilAKCd0CbPyyKwWgb7cGNJdKAbY2cmg5OVD6okGNXKY0OQ\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzIhVRDsG_y0dEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
